title: EUREKA Encyclopedia
description:
Product Description:

Eureka is a complete, compact encyclopedia, containing over 300,000 entries on everything from the Big Bang to the End of Days, and everything in between. A wholly new conception in encyclopedic knowledge, Eureka allows standard access to entries via powerful search and alphabetized index, but it also allows users to browse through whole thematic categories: entries are organized according to their thematic connections.

Eureka offers concise entries, reaching a level of precision unachieved by any other resource. Thematic categories include Science, Leisure, Agriculture, Technology, Culture, and much, much more.

Brought to you by Ultralingua, the makers of the Ultralingua dictionaries.
Operating System Requirements:

This product is designed to run on the following operating systems:
Mac OS X 10.3
Mac OS X 10.2
Additional Requirements:
Mac OS X 10.2 or higher
must have Safari installed.
